name: Streets of Beirut — 03
description:
Beirut is a city in constant evolution. True commercial, political, financial and cultural center of the Middle East, known for its lively nightlife, Beirut is a cosmopolitan playground where so many different nationalities and heterogeneous faiths coexist. Series exploring the streets of the city I did doing a daily routine walks during a week (2019). It includes urban geography, architectural contrasts of past and present, the communities, street life…
